{"tid":492233,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"比特幣耗電量驚人，虛擬貨幣網路耗電量，接近香港全城的耗電量","createTime":"2017-12-07T10:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T03:00:10.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6c231a2153fc598117c5d2e1ecf0d136b717860a","tid":492233,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"比特幣耗電量驚人，整個加密貨幣耗電量，接近香港全城的耗電量<br />\n<br />\n比特幣單次的交易(single transaction)，耗電量相等於一個美國家庭 8 天的耗電量。<br />\n<br />\n整個比特幣網路，耗電量已超越google 所有 datacentre 的耗電量。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣耗電量是 整個visa payment network 的 60倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171127/mobile/bkn-20171127170748319-1127_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171127170748319-1127_00842_001.html&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6ngdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=3f90a7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171127/mobile/bkn-20171127170748319-1127_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.trad.cn.rfi.fr/生態/20171129-比特幣交易耗電驚人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.trad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B%2F20171129-%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E8%80%97%E9%9B%BB%E9%A9%9A%E4%BA%BA&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6ngdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=9213e85f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.trad.cn.rfi.fr/生態/20171129-比特幣交易耗電驚人</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://digiconomist.net/ethereum-energy-consumption\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigiconomist.net%2Fethereum-energy-consumption&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6ngdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=de23a0bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://digiconomist.net/ethereum-energy-consumption</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://digiconomist.net/bitcoin-energy-consumption\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdigiconomist.net%2Fbitcoin-energy-consumption&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6ngdLCpCjo