lockchain, peer to peer<br />\n<br />\n2 Bitcoin網路耗電勁，<br />\n因為有樣叫bitcoin mining，<br />\n靠耗用cpu和gpu資源計數對撞，去mine bitcoin。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，有d hacker會hack人部電腦來mine bitcoin, 偷走人家的電腦cpu或gpu資訊。<br />\n<br />\n有些bitcoin礦場，就走社會漏洞或行賄，唔俾電費，借用發電廠電力去mine bitcoin"},{"pid":"e69a459e8d80b92cfa9fd76defcb4498ce21c1a9","tid":492233,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:00:10.000Z","msg":"浪費電力計埋啲垃圾數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}